              <td class="events">
                <h3><a class="anchor" id="top" name="sraagm"></a>Sanderstead Residents' Association AGM. Wednesday 8th May</h3>
                <p>NOTICE OF THE ANNUAL GENERAL MEETING. 8 pm on Wednesday, 8 May 2019. At ALL SAINTS’ CHURCH HALL Onslow Gardens, Sanderstead, Surrey.</p>
                <p>Notice is hereby given of the Annual General Meeting of the Association. At the meeting the Officers and Executive Committee will be elected.  Nominations for the committee should be sent to the Hon Secretary 14 days prior to the AGM. Your committee would like to see as many members as possible support this AGM.</p>
                <p>AGENDA
                <ul>
                  <li>Welcome by Chairman, Mr Dennis King</li>
                  <li>Apologies Received</li>
                  <li>Minutes of the AGM held on 10 May 2018</li>
                  <li>Secretary’s Report</li>
                  <li>Treasurer’s Report</li>
                  <li>Election of Officers and Executive Committee</li>
                  <li>Presentation of cheques</li>
                  <li>Any other business</li>
                </ul>
              </p>
              <p>Our Sanderstead Safer Neighbouthood Police Team have been invited, along with our MP Chris Philp, GLA member Steve O'Connell and our local councillors.</p>
              <p>Drinks and refreshments will available at the close of the AGM.  It’s an opportunity to discuss  issues with your local councillors and committee.</p>
                </td>
                <td class="events"><%= link_to image_tag("small-images/residents_logo100.jpg", alt: "SRA logo"), "http://www.sanderstead-residents.co.uk" %></td>
            </tr>

