                <h3><a class="anchor" id="top" name="rotaryband"></a>Rotary Big Band Concert, Friday 14th June</h3>
                <p>Rotary Club of Croydon Jubilee presents the Jubilee Big Band Night featuring the Nigel Garrard Orchestra. Friday 14th June, Warlingham Rugby Club, Limpsfield Road, Warlingham,  CR6 9RB. Doors open 7.15pm. Tickets £16, children under 15 £12. Principal Surplus donated to Alzheimer's Society, the remainder to local charities. No tickets on sale at the door, phone or email David Cronk. Phone: 01883 819 087. Email: beacronk@hotmail.com</p>
              </td>
