                <h3><a class="anchor" id="top" name="sugandh"></a>Piano Recital in aid of Sugandh, Saturday 15th June at 7.30pm</h3>
                  <p>Piano Recital by Verity Brooks, Sat 15th June 2019, 7pm for 7:30pm. At All Saints’ Church, Onslow Gardens, Sanderstead CR2 9AB. Drinks and refreshments will be served from 7pm. Entry on the door - please give generously to support the work of Sugandh. Verity’s programme will include works by Chopin, Liszt, Beethoven and Schubert. <%= link_to "More information", "resource/verity_sugsndh.pdf" %></p>
                  <p>All proceeds from this recital will go to Sugandh, New Delhi, a grass roots charity working among marginalized communities in the city. Sugandh supports children to stay in school though tuition and empowers women through self-help groups. <%= link_to "www.sugandh.org", "http://www.sugandh.org" %></p>
              </td>
